parameters: \n<\n[1]>I can't leave like this.\.\. I need to wear my \iw[1] and \ia[101]...
"These \iw[1] are perfect for defending yourself in the wild area around End City!"
"Make sure you don't forget to wear them AGAIN,\. dumb cat!\.\. Use \i[544] to attack and hold it down to charge the powerful spin attack I came up with."
"But just avoid getting into fights,\. if you can.\.\. Despite all the airs,\. you're WEAK compared to the monsters that come up from the Hole,\. Sis!"
"And you're forbidden from trying them inside the house!\.\. Remember what happened last time?!"
It's your bed.\.\. Nothing fancy,\. but it's clean.
\n<\n[1]>This is no time to go back to sleep.\.\. Where's that kid gone during a night like this?
\n<\n[1]>His pillow...\.\.\. Why is it on the floor?
"We're out of fruit!\.\. Go fetch some tomorrow,\. useless furry!"
